snippet.title: Mega Alien Destroyer (Trailer) (PC shoot em up)
snippet.description:
Mega Alien Destroyer it's an action packed shoot em up, with distinct zones, a challenging difficulty and huge alien bosses and machines, inspired in the classic shooters of the 80's and 90's like R-Type, Contra series, Alien Soldier, Eliminate Down, Gynoug and others.

Download at
http://julianmartinezgames.itch.io

Download soundtrack at 
http://julianmartinez.bandcamp.com

Programming, design, art, soundtrack, everything by Julián Martínez.
